  Add USE flag description to metadata as per GLEP 56.

  18 May 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> gnugadu-2.2.6-r1.ebuild,
  gnugadu-2.3.0.ebuild:
  Move pkgconfig, automake, gettext, and others to DEPEND.

  12 Jan 2008; Michał Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> -gnugadu-2.2.8.ebuild,
  -gnugadu-2.2.9.ebuild:
  Remove old ebuilds.

