  Fix quoting issues, remove unused dependencies.

  12 Jan 2008; Michał Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> gnugadu-2.3.0.ebuild:
  Fix bug #205499.

  22 Jul 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> gnugadu-2.2.8.ebuild,
